    <article class="blog-post">
        <header>
            <h1>Vaccination Preachers</h1>
            <div class="lead-image">
                <img src="/images/article-details/250_Vaccination-Preachers.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <div class="meta clearfix">
                    <div class="author">
                        <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
                        <span class="data">Manidhara Das</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="date">
                        <i class="fa fa-calendar"></i>
                        <span class="data">30 Nov 2021</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="comments">
                        <i class="fa fa-comments"></i>
                        <span class="data"><a href="#comments">2 Comments</a></span>
                    </div>                                
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="body"><p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">What the vaccination preachers are actually telling us:</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">Get vaccinated!</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">1/ Not the law of karma decides our future, but scientists do.<br />
Ignorant as we are, we must accept what the scientists put on the market! They know what we don&acute;t know..</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />
2/ Your body doesn&acute;t belong to Krsna, but actually to yourself.<br />
Herewith you can inject any chemical into your body scientists offer as you are the owner and you can do with your body what you like.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />
3/ Accept whatever &bdquo;scientists&ldquo; offer blindly.<br />
They know what they are doing, it is only for your best.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />
4/ Devotional service is not ahaituky apratihata, but it depends on the way your body works and the way it is maintained.<br />
Even not being affected by disease, take preventive measures and take shelter in vaccination as it is the remedy scientists offer, and not Krsna&acute;s sweet will which will define our future.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">5/ Scientists can override Krsna&acute;s will by dint of vaccination.<br />
They are god, not Krsna.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">As one of the foremost vaccination propagators was praised by a foolish admirer, &bdquo;Maharaja, you are always ahead of time!&ldquo;<br />
Indeed, this mathaji was right. Maharaja is ahead of time in Kali Yuga, speeding it up by his foolish arrogant appeal, urging us to believe and follow whatever the scientists offer.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">And there are some who go even so far that they dare to use Srila Prabhupada as vaccination advertisement. Don&acute;t they know that Srila Prabhupada, who was known for being most skeptical about the medical treatments He was getting, said:</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&bdquo;Never bring me to a hospital&ldquo;, and</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&bdquo;Western medical treatment is only needles, needles, needles. That&acute;s all they can do.&ldquo;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><br />
We know that in order to be able to preach Srila Prabhupada was once or twice vaccinated. He Himself mentions it ironically in one of His lectures. That kind of vaccination was an entirely different type of vaccine then we get today.<br />
There is a massive testimony from doctors who worked their whole life in medical profession how devastating effects these current vaccines can have on the human organism. (One of them, the chief of the biggest hospital in Chemnitz, Germany, just committed suicide, not being able to sustain the pressure of his conscience while being forced heavily by his superiors to advertise and apply today&acute;s vaccines. He left behind a devastating detailed letter describing it and how corrupt the medical industry is.)</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">The effects of these chemicals injected into human bodies may be visible in years to come, of course, covered up by the demoniac media or defined as &bdquo;new mutation&ldquo; of the great deadly virus.<br />
The lies we are bombarded with are already of such primitive kind that even the simple man on the street cannot believe them. However, some of our ISKCON dignitaries do believe this demoniac propaganda and take part in demoniac plans of the present leaders.<br />
Herewith they risk something far worse than being infected by the big virus - they risk to go to the hellish planets for a considerable time in order to experience what it means to misguide others.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">All glories to those devotees who don&acute;t hesitate to quote Bhagavad-gita where Krsna describes the nature of demons and the work they are engaged in, in great detail.<br />
Everybody is urged to read His words and see how they are put into action by the present leaders of society, who are nothing else than demons or puppets in the hands of demons.</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
</div>
    </article>

